n that matter, but how much help are you really willing to exert if all your time is for not.  I will sit here and congratulate those you out there that can get a group of friends together at the drop of a hat to help you with anything you need.  But honestly folks, how many friends like do you really think you have? (of course, aside from real life friends that play together)  <br><br>Don't take this too hard folks, it is after all just a game.  Sorry if these posts offended some people, but some people make statements I am positive cannot be supported.  You can claim all sorts of grandiose righteous acts of valor you want, but when it comes down to crunch time, who truly doesnt look out for themselves first.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
