l, how is anyone going to get this type of stuff, if everyone on their server hates them :).<br><br>Long-winded and unfocused as I may seem, *I* at least understand my ramblings.<br><br>--Cafeen<br>--Tier'Dal Enchanter<br>--Officer of the Azure Storm<br>--Luclin Server<br>&nbsp;<br>Cafeen<br>Tier'Dal Beguiler<br>Officer of Azure Storm<br>Luclin Server<br><br>"Feen Down!"<br>"Woot! It's an official raid now!"</td></tr>
